{"text": " A year ago, I choreographed this dance. I've been traveling to various live nation amphitheaters to prove that this dance is the perfect dance to dance to any genre of music. Up next, we're going to the Hollywood casino amphitheater in St. Louis to see Odessa. So first I headed over to the green room. They offer complimentary wine, draft beer, and popcorn. I decided to grab myself a liquid death sparkling water, and they had a private air-conditioned restroom, which was really cool. And then I headed over to the lawn terrace, which offered beautiful views of the concert, and I grabbed another liquid death water, and enjoyed the views. Here is some footage of the concert, it was really fun, and I did my signature dance.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 0.0, "end": 1.76, "text": " A year ago, I choreographed this dance.", "tokens": [50364, 316, 1064, 2057, 11, 286, 14625, 3108, 292, 341, 4489, 13, 50452], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21042142595563615, "compression_ratio": 1.6042402826855124, "no_speech_prob": 0.003306535305455327}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 1.76, "end": 5.04, "text": " I've been traveling to various live nation amphitheaters to prove that this dance is the", "tokens": [50452, 286, 600, 668, 9712, 281, 3683, 1621, 4790, 40077, 45381, 16749, 281, 7081, 300, 341, 4489, 307, 264, 50616], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21042142595563615, "compression_ratio": 1.6042402826855124, "no_speech_prob": 0.003306535305455327}, {"id": 2, "seek": 0, "start": 5.04, "end": 7.640000000000001, "text": " perfect dance to dance to any genre of music.", "tokens": [50616, 2176, 4489, 281, 4489, 281, 604, 11022, 295, 1318, 13, 50746], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.21042142595563615, "compression_ratio": 1.6042402826855124, "no_speech_prob": 0.003306535305455327}, {"id": 3, "seek": 0, "start": 7.640000000000001, "end": 11.88, "text": " Up next, we're going to the Hollywood casino amphitheater in St. Louis to see Odessa.", "to